<script>
document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", () => {
  const nameEl = document.getElementById("user-name-display");
  const visitCountEl = document.getElementById("visit-count");
  let userName = localStorage.getItem("userFirstName") || "Guest";
  let visits = parseInt(localStorage.getItem("visitCount")) || 0;
  visits++;
  localStorage.setItem("visitCount", visits);
  if (nameEl) nameEl.textContent = userName;
  if (visitCountEl) visitCountEl.textContent = visits;

  // Clock & Location
  const clockEl = document.getElementById("clock");
  const locEl = document.getElementById("location");
  setInterval(() => { clockEl.textContent = new Date().toLocaleTimeString(); }, 1000);
  if (navigator.geolocation) {
    navigator.geolocation.getCurrentPosition(pos => { locEl.textContent = `Lat: ${pos.coords.latitude.toFixed(2)}, Long: ${pos.coords.longitude.toFixed(2)}`; },
      () => { locEl.textContent = "Location unavailable"; });
  }
});
